---
title: Middle Eastern Pork & Feta-Sumac Potatoes with Roasted Eggplant, Tomato-Mint Salsa & Garlic Dip
description: We could pretend the main attraction here is the tender roasted eggplant with refreshing mint, or the succulent spiced pork, but
that’d be dishonest. If we’re being real, the magic in this dish is the stunning sumac roasted potatoes delicately topped with a
smattering of feta. It's crispy, filling, earthy and indulgent. We could go on and on, but we’ll let you get on with the eating.
